    "text": "老師這題一口氣問了三個問題",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 31.42,
    "end": 34.96,
    "speaker": "曉臻",
    "text": "我光看題目就覺得頭暈目眩了",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 35.16,
    "end": 38.86,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "戰士們深呼吸我們一題一題來",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 39.06,
    "end": 42.58,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "題目說這杯糖水溶解度是",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 42.78,
    "end": 46.24,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "$\\frac{20\\text{g}}{100\\text{g}\\text{水}}$",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": [
      "$\\frac{20\\text{g}}{100\\text{g}\\text{水}}$"
    ]
  },
  {
    "start": 46.44,
    "end": 50.02,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "第一題問兩百克的水加進去",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 50.22,
    "end": 53.76,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "最多可以溶解多少克溶質",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 53.96,
    "end": 58.05,
    "speaker": "曉臻",
    "text": "這個我會 純水變成了兩倍",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 58.25,
    "end": 61.71,
    "speaker": "曉臻",
    "text": "那麼胃口當然也跟著變兩倍啦",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 61.91,
    "end": 65.52,
    "speaker": "曉臻",
    "text": "所以二十乘以二就等於四十",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 65.72,
    "end": 70.55,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "沒錯 第一題的正確答案是",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 70.75,
    "end": 74.46,
